The paper proposes a data representation model that uses nsNMF for hierarchical feature learning. This involves extending the unit algorithm into several layers. The experiments conducted involve document and image data, which suggests that the paper could belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), information retrieval (cs.IR), computational linguistics (cs.CL), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
